message.body: I got some biscuits and chicken for you if you want it
Yeh that would be good. I'm going to be home in an hour or so
I put it in the fridge. You have all of it
Have you spoke with James about the incense?

I did and about the stuff in the living room and the mannequin. It seems he is trying to provoke me by ignoring me. I need to get the rent from him for next month before i give him 60 days notice. You can mention to him about the incense and the stuff in the living room and say that I also asked him in an email and in person if you want. But he is pretty much getting booted
If that's the case I won't bring it up
There's a big ham in the fridge if you want to have any of it
